522
00:28:22,493 --> 00:28:25,078
All right, young lady,
we'll give it a shot, see how it goes.

523
00:28:25,121 --> 00:28:27,664
Good. My name's Valerie.

524
00:28:27,707 --> 00:28:30,750
Very well, Valerie.

525
00:28:30,793 --> 00:28:33,920
This is Troy,
