533
00:28:51,522 --> 00:28:53,022
Well, it was nice meeting you.

534
00:28:56,444 --> 00:28:57,485
Thank you.

535
00:28:59,989 --> 00:29:04,534
From the shining se-ee-ea...

536
00:29:06,495 --> 00:29:09,205
