574
00:30:43,133 --> 00:30:45,093
Okay, I'm gonna go.

575
00:30:45,135 --> 00:30:46,886
This was fun. It was nice.

576
00:30:46,929 --> 00:30:51,015
So I'm gonna go freshen up
for our big night out.

577
00:30:51,058 --> 00:30:53,101
I'll see you at dinner.

578
00:31:01,569 --> 00:31:05,321
I can't believe that you know
Sulu from "Star Trek."

579
